name: Girl In The Bucket Hat Genesis
description:
Syaeeza Liana, 2021

‘Girl in the Bucket Hat’ is a depiction of being happy but still very shy to show one’s true- self. It also shows the limit of expression one holds towards themselves. Sometimes, we know we can show and do more but we build a wall in front of us. We may never reach the top but it keeps us safe and happy with the way it is. 

Please visit www.pinktank.art for more information.
